## 🎨 **Design Requirements**

### **🎯 User Experience Goals**
- **Inclusive**: Accessible to all users
- **Compliant**: WCAG 2.1 AAA compliant
- **Flexible**: Adaptable to different needs
- **Intuitive**: Easy to use with assistive technology
- **Consistent**: Uniform accessibility across all pages

### **🔧 Technical Requirements**
- **ARIA**: Proper ARIA labels and roles
- **Semantic HTML**: Semantic markup
- **Keyboard**: Full keyboard support
- **Screen Reader**: Screen reader optimization
- **Performance**: Fast assistive technology support

